body_html:
@beew @aaroey This compilation issue was fixed and merged to master on 9/18:
08af8ca
By that time the release branch for 1.11 was already cut - so this fix is not available in the 1.11.0 release.

However, if you pick up the latest master or the next TensorFlow release - this will go away. Please let us know if you have any questions/comments.

body:
@beew @aaroey This compilation issue was fixed and merged to master on 9/18:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/08af8cac22af4cc430e092b6218ca77736efb82c
By that time the release branch for 1.11 was already cut - so this fix is not available in the 1.11.0 release. 

However, if you pick up the latest master or the next TensorFlow release - this will go away. Please let us know if you have any questions/comments.
